bbs.details:
development of the portal for processing billing data ("Universal Payment Bills", receipts and other payment documents);
creation of interface and server part of the module for processing PDF files according to a given template, creation of the module for generating attendant documentation;
creation of web-interface and web-components for generating reports, managing statuses and routes of orders, sending email notifications to customers;
switching to the esbuild build tool, which is more adapted to the React-Golang application stack, build time was reduced by more than 20 times and the build size by 2.5 times;
creation of services for updating database of post offices, combining documents with subsequent printing, automated output of labels and application of technical marks;
creation of web-interface of the transport-logistics module.

iif.details:
development of the client-server simulation model of the communication system as part of scientific project;
development of the system for gathering and processing information to rate the functioning of the complex of technical means for perimeter protection;
development of desktop- and web-interfaces for managing the security complex and its interaction with peripheral devices;
finding solutions for being able to produce main blocks of security systems, searching for potential manufacturers and suppliers;
full architectural supervision of the production cycle, coordination of work between departments.
